Package: CONCERTDR
Type: Package
Title: Drug Response Data Analysis Using CMap Database
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Hengxin Pan <pan.h@wehi.edu.au>
Maintainer: Hengxin Pan <pan.h@wehi.edu.au>
Description: Provides tools for drug response data analysis with a focus on 
    the Connectivity Map (CMap) database. It enables researchers to extract, 
    process, and analyze drug response signatures from experimental data and 
    match them against reference profiles from CMap. The package includes 
    functions for parameter extraction, combination generation, data processing 
    from GCTX files, and various signature matching methods including 
    Kolmogorov-Smirnov, GSEA-based, and others.
